Compile OpenDDS as usual.

In ${OPENDDS_HOME}/DevGuideExamples/DCPS/Messenger/ directory,
  - copy rtps.ini to ${OPENDDS_HOME}/DevGuideExamples/DCPS/Messenger/
    to be easily accessible by samples      
  - run publisher with command
      > . ${OPENDDS_HOME}/setenv.sh
      > ./publisher -DCPSConfigFile rtps.ini
  - run subscriber with command
      > . ${OPENDDS_HOME}/setenv.sh
      > ./subscriber -DCPSConfigFile rtps.ini
  